Interface ILoggerModel

All Superinterfaces:
BasicLogModel
All Known Implementing Classes:
LoggerModel
public interface ILoggerModel extends BasicLogModel
Extends the BasicLogModel to add functionality for managing the visibility of different log levels. Provides methods to enable or disable the display of specific types of log messages.
